overview: You be embarkin' on a journey of six salty tales including Gary and his new obsession, a nasty sea urchin at the Krusty Krab, a lesson in kah-rah-tay for Squidward, a few Kraby Patty formula theft attempts, and a cat that's roaming Bikini Bottom.
title: SpongeBob SquarePants: Bizarro Bikini Bottom
